    "To achieve this, the XLNet encoder is employed for sentence representation, while the Bi-LSTM and attention pooling layer are utilized to encode and learn paragraph representations.",
    "The private layer, on the other hand, is responsible for learning trait-specific representations.",
    "This layer incorporates trait-to-trait interaction and augments traits with more relevant features to enhance the essay representation for each task.",
    "The work emphasizes the significance of enriching the original essay representation with trait-specific features.",
    "The interaction among traits is captured using attention mechanisms, resulting in improved overall and trait-specific scores."
